  "title": "Gingerly Peppery Thai Tofu Pad Thai",
  "description": "A spicy and savory Thai dish featuring tofu, infused oil, and a blend of peppers, perfect for a sick day pick-me-up, diabetic-friendly and served on a slate tile.",
