  "instructions": [
    "Heat the infused oil in a large skillet or wok over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the tofu and cook until golden brown, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the sliced red bell pepper and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Add the cooked rice noodles, green onions, and chopped cilantro to the skillet.",
    "Pour in the lime juice and stir to combine.",
    "Add the salt, black pepper, and grated ginger, and stir-fry for 1 minute.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Transfer the Pad Thai to a slate tile and serve immediately."
